nodes.text: Squick was a male Trandoshan who, by c. 19 BBY, had became a member of a group of Believers on the planet Genarius, under the command of Alina Impeveri.
Despite not being a Force-sensitive, Squick wanted to become a Jedi. He wore Jedi robes that he had looted from a Jedi corpse, and obtained a lightsaber, which he learned how to use.
